org.gvsig.raster.postgis.swing

Interface PostGISRasterSwingManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultPostGISRasterSwingManager

    public interface PostGISRasterSwingManager
    This class is responsible of the management of the library's swing user interface. It is the swing library's main entry point, and provides all the services to manage library swing components.
    See Also:
    PostGISRasterWindowManager, JValidationServicePanel
